::Ramulus/Grimmler::

Grimmler nods. "I'll go to the Cybertronian Fire," he says, turning 
around and activating his jetpack, "We have lots of supplies, but I'm 
not sure if they'll be compatible with this time period.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus glances back at Mangus, still looking at Fliq and Brix.

"I'll go to the Alliance," he says to Mangus, "Zardus owes me a facor 
back from the old days."

He turns back to Fliq, waiting for the bot to answer his last 
question.
